title: 11/02/21 DPS Best Of

description:
On Today's Dan Patrick Show, DP recaps last night's Chiefs/Giants game. Should last night actually feel like a win for the Chiefs? FS1's Nick Wright calls in to explain why the Cowboys are the real deal. And ESPN's Ryan Clark tells us what the Rams acquisition of Von Miller means.
